# Mapbox Configuration

# Get your free Mapbox token from: https://account.mapbox.com/auth/signin/
# 1. Create a Mapbox account at https://account.mapbox.com/
# 2. Navigate to your tokens page at https://account.mapbox.com/tokens/
# 3. Copy your default public token
# 4. Paste it below:

VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.your_token_here

# For developing locally, you can also set it via CLI:
# VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.your_token_here npm run dev
